docs {
  # Mobily Provider
  
  All Mobily-specific TMF622 orders and journey requests. Shared workflows
  (WFM CPE/ME, TMF641, SingleView) live under `Shared-Workflows/`.
  
  Journeys: Activation, Relocation, Device-Swap, Upgrade, Downgrade, Suspend,
  Termination, Rewiring, Maintenance, Request-Update, Installation-Failure,
  Mesh-Extender-Standalone.
}

